OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781542111
OL,3,CLetters written by Hull-born William
OL,4,CWilberforce fetch #3.9k under the
OL,5,Chammer
OL,7,FTwo letters written by anti-slavery
OL,8,Fcampaigner William Wilberforce fetched
OL,9,Fnearly #4,000 at auction.
OL,11,FThe Hull-born anti-slavery campaigner
OL,12,Fis one of the most influential
OL,13,Fpoliticians in British history, best
OL,14,Fknown as a prominent voice in
OL,15,Fabolishing the slave trade.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
