PN,33302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781542111
OL,3,CLetters written by Hull-born William
OL,4,CWilberforce fetch #3.9k under the
OL,5,Chammer
OL,7,FSpanning across 17 years of his life,
OL,8,Fthe letters were sent to close friends
OL,9,FAdmiral Sir Sidney Smith in September
OL,10,F1814 and the Marquis of Wellesley in
OL,11,FMay 1831 and offer rarely seen
OL,12,Finsights into his personality and
OL,13,Fpassions.
OL,15,FBoth letters run at six pages long and
OL,16,Fwere put up for auction by
OL,17,FWilberforce's great-great-great
OL,18,Fgrandson, Charles Maxsted.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781542111
OL,3,CLetters written by Hull-born William
OL,4,CWilberforce fetch #3.9k under the
OL,5,Chammer
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Calendar, he said,
OL,8,F"There were a whole lot of old letters
OL,9,Fwe didn't pay attention to them quite
OL,10,Ffrankly. Then I thought I wonder what
OL,11,Fthis is."
OL,13,FThe letters were sold at Hawleys
OL,14,FAntique and Fine Art Auction on
OL,15,FSaturday 13 June.
OL,17,FThe auctioneer Caroline Hawley said,
OL,18,F"It's taken an awful long time to
OL,19,Ftranscribe these letters... but they
OL,20,Fare both fascinating.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781542111
OL,3,CLetters written by Hull-born William
OL,4,CWilberforce fetch #3.9k under the
OL,5,Chammer
OL,7,F"We've had so much interest not only
OL,8,Ffrom the UK but from America and so
OL,9,Fmany places.
OL,11,F"I don't know where they're going to
OL,12,Fend up."
OL,14,FThe documents present an interesting
OL,15,Fside to Wilberforce, who died in 1833,
OL,16,Fas these are personal letters written
OL,17,Fto his close friends.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
